    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竞速、碰撞、爆炸、逃离外星人。升级你的汽车。换一辆新的。碾压路人。躲避鲨鱼。飞跃跳台。尽情享受吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/ee8538d756474baadc35390f63d194c0.poster.avif?t=1760574627\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/ee8538d756474baadc35390f63d194c0.webm?t=1760574627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/ee8538d756474baadc35390f63d194c0.mp4?t=1760574627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏模式：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>街头竞速</strong>：在有交通和行人的街道上竞速</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/58cf984c89ccbcaf93f4ee6550f75985.poster.avif?t=1760574627\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/58cf984c89ccbcaf93f4ee6550f75985.webm?t=1760574627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/58cf984c89ccbcaf93f4ee6550f75985.mp4?t=1760574627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡竞赛</strong>：撞击行人并到达检查点以提高分数</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/0f2c63f37840f9797ad76f91d38508b3.poster.avif?t=1760574627\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219800/extras/0f2c6